143	26	สนามกีฬาอเนกประสงค์หญ้าเทียม ทางเลือกที่ดีกว่าสำหรับโรงเรียนยุคใหม่	blog-news-7060-x	2025-08-06 07:26:04.467+00	t	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "ในยุคที่โรงเรียนให้ความสำคัญกับกิจกรรมกลางแจ้งและการเสริมสร้างพัฒนาการของนักเรียนในทุกมิติ “สนามกีฬา” กลายเป็นสิ่งสำคัญที่ช่วยยกระดับคุณภาพการเรียนรู้ แต่สนามหญ้าจริงกลับมีปัญหามากมาย ทั้งดูแลยาก พื้นลื่น และไม่ปลอดภัยในฤดูฝน ทางเลือกใหม่อย่าง ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "สนามกีฬาอเนกประสงค์หญ้าเทียม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " จึงได้รับความนิยมอย่างมาก โดยเฉพาะในกลุ่ม ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "โรงเรียนเอกชน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " และ ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "โรงเรียนนานาชาติ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "horizontalrule", "version": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "สนามกีฬาอเนกประสงค์คืออะไร?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "สนามกีฬาอเนกประสงค์คือพื้นที่กิจกรรมที่สามารถรองรับการใช้งานหลากหลายประเภท เช่น ฟุตบอล วอลเลย์บอล กิจกรรมกลางแจ้ง หรือใช้จัดงานโรงเรียน จุดเด่นคือ ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "การออกแบบที่ยืดหยุ่นและทนทาน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " รองรับการใช้งานหนักและใช้ได้ตลอดทั้งปี", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เมื่อเลือกใช้ ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "พื้นสนามหญ้าเทียม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ที่เหมาะสม พื้นที่นั้นจะปลอดภัย ดูแลรักษาง่าย และลดเวลาในการปรับปรุงบ่อยครั้ง", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "horizontalrule", "version": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "จุดเด่นของหญ้าเทียมในสนามโรงเรียน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " 1. ปลอดภัยต่อเด็ก", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "หญ้าเทียมของ About Grass ออกแบบให้มีความนุ่มพิเศษ ลดแรงกระแทกจากการล้ม เหมาะกับเด็กทุกช่วงวัย โดยเฉพาะเด็กเล็กที่ยังไม่คล่องตัว รวมถึงลดการเกิดภูมิแพ้ในกรณีกลุ่มเด็กที่มีการแพ้เกสรดอกไม้", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " 2. ประหยัดงบประมาณระยะยาว", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "ไม่ต้องรดน้ำ ไม่ต้องตัดหญ้า ไม่ต้องจ้างคนดูแลสนามอย่างต่อเนื่อง — ช่วยลดต้นทุนโรงเรียนได้อย่างมหาศาล", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "3. ใช้งานได้ทุกฤดูกาล", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "หญ้าเทียมทนแดด ทนฝน ไม่มีปัญหาโคลนหรือน้ำขัง เด็กสามารถใช้งานได้ต่อเนื่องโดยไม่ต้องกังวลเรื่องสภาพอากาศ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "4. เสริมภาพลักษณ์ทันสมัย", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "สนามที่เขียวขจีตลอดปี ช่วยให้โรงเรียนดูสะอาด เป็นมืออาชีพ และน่าเชื่อถือต่อผู้ปกครอง", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "horizontalrule", "version": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เหมาะกับใคร?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "โรงเรียนทั่วไป", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ที่ต้องการอัปเกรดสนามกีฬาให้ดูดีและปลอดภัย", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "โรงเรียนนานาชาติ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ที่ต้องการพื้นที่กิจกรรมมาตรฐานสูง", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "ศูนย์การเรียนรู้เอกชน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " หรือสถานรับเลี้ยงเด็กที่ต้องการความปลอดภัยสูงสุด", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "horizontalrule", "version": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "วิธีเลือกหญ้าเทียมสำหรับโรงเรียน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "การเลือกหญ้าเทียมสำหรับโรงเรียนควรคำนึงถึง 3 ปัจจัยหลัก:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " ความนุ่ม & ความหนา", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เลือกวัสดุที่ซับแรงกระแทกได้ดี เพื่อความปลอดภัยสูงสุดสำหรับเด็ก", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " ระบบระบายน้ำ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "ต้องมีระบบระบายน้ำที่ดี เพื่อหลีกเลี่ยงการเกิดน้ำขังและความชื้นสะสม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": " มาตรฐานความปลอดภัย", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "วัสดุทุกชิ้นควรผ่านการรับรอง เช่น ปลอดสารตะกั่ว และไม่ลื่นเมื่อน้ำเปียก", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "horizontalrule", "version": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "บริการจาก About Grass", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "About Grass มีบริการครบวงจร ตั้งแต่การวางแผน ออกแบบ ไปจนถึงการติดตั้งสนามกีฬาหญ้าเทียม โดยทีมงานมืออาชีพ พร้อม ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "รับประกันคุณภาพทั้งวัสดุและงานติดตั้ง", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "บริการของเรา:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode"