, "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1. โซนนั่งเล่นล้อมด้วยต้นไม้สูง", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "ปลูกปาล์ม ไทร กระบองเพชรขนาดใหญ่ ช่วยเพิ่มร่มเงาและความเป็นส่วนตัว", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2. สวนกระถางมินิมอลสไตล์คาเฟ่", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เลือกกระถางโทนสีเดียว เช่น ขาว เทา ดำ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "\\t", "type": "tab", "style": "", "detail": 2, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "จัดระดับต้นไม้ให้มีหลายระดับเพื่อสร้างมิติ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "3. จัดทางเดินด้วยไม้เทียมคู่กับหญ้าเทียม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เพิ่มความสวยงาม ดูอบอุ่น และใช้งานง่าย", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "4. สวนแนวตั้ง (Vertical Garden)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "เหมาะสำหรับดาดฟ้าพื้นที่น้อย เพิ่มความเขียวแบบไม่กินพื้นที่", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h3", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "5. สวนสไตล์ญี่ปุ่น (Zen Garden)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "ใช้กรวดเทา หินธรรมชาติ พุ่ม矮 ร่วมกับหญ้าเทียมให้ความรู้สึกสงบ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "h2", "type": "heading", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "สรุปเปลี่ยนดาดฟ้าร้อน ๆ ให้เป็นสวนสวยได้ง่ายกว่าที่คิด", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "การจัดสวนบนดาดฟ้าไม่ใช่เรื่องยาก หากเข้าใจสภาพพื้นที่และเลือกต้นไม้–หญ้าที่เหมาะสม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "หญ้าเทียม", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " ถือเป็นตัวช่วยสำคัญที่ช่วยให้สวนดาดฟ้าดูสวยเป็นธรรมชาติ ดูแลง่าย และใช้งานได้ยาวนาน", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0,